remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-102">スマート ラベルを有効にすると、グラフには、一連のユーザー定義のルールに基づいて、重複するデータ ポイント ラベルが再配置します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-103">データ ポイント ラベルをリンクする引き出し線が描画されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-104">引き出し線の表示属性を制御できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-105">これらの視覚属性には、色、線のスタイル、および線の幅が含まれます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>と<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>プロパティは、装飾などの引き出し線の最後に表示される矢印などを制御します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-107"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A>にプロパティを設定できる<xref:System.Drawing.Color>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-108">色を設定する引き出し線の色を設定した場合も自動的には、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>とによって定義された装飾、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-109"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A>プロパティは、引き出し線のピクセルの幅を制御します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-110">このプロパティの使用の装飾をスケーリングしても、 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> 、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-111">スマート ラベルの移動は、いくつかの動きに関連するプロパティを使用して制御できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-112">移動の方向の距離の規則を定義し、プロット エリアのままにするラベルが許可されているデータ ポイントであるかどうか。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-113">既定の動作規則では、ほとんどの問題が解決通常されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-114"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>データからのピクセル単位で最大距離は、ポイントのデータ ポイント ラベルが重なる場合に移動する許可されることを示す値を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-115"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>プロパティは、最小距離 (ピクセル単位)、データからポイントのデータ ポイント ラベルが重なる場合移動されることを指定する値を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-116">ラベルはあるが、データ ポイント ラベルを再配置する必要がありますし、指定したピクセルの数以上で移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-117"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>プロパティは、重なりの問題を解決できないときに、ラベルを非表示にするかどうかを示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-118">場合、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>プロパティは`true`で指定された領域内のデータ ポイントを描画することはできませんと<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>と<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>で許可されている方向で<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>、データ ポイント ラベルは描画されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-119"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>プロパティは、データ ポイント ラベルを移動できる方向を定義します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-120">このプロパティでは 1 つ<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>値または複数のビットごとの OR<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>値。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="387cd-121">既定値はすべてのビット演算 OR<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>値、ポイント、データの中央に点を除いて、すべての可能な方向に再配置が可能にします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="387cd-122">スマート ラベルは、次のグラフの種類はサポートされません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="387cd-123">横棒グラフ: バーと 100% 積み上げ横棒グラフ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="387cd-124">図形グラフ: ドーナツ グラフ、極座標、レーダー グラフ、円します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="387cd-125">範囲グラフ: 範囲、範囲縦棒および範囲横棒グラフ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="387cd-126">積み上げ面グラフ: 積み上げ領域と 100% 積み上げ面グラフ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="387cd-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
